    {
      "content": "这还算好的了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我带团那两次真的什么人都见过了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "有次一个大爷拍照的时候手机掉河里了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "大爷非要我去给他捞起来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我真无语了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "把导游当超人使了么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是说啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "这还不算最奇葩的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "还有情侣在旅行的时候吵架让我去调解",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "最后害得我们整个团都当他们的恋爱npc了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "在网上看多了骂旅行社",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "还是第一次听到导游的视角",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "唉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的很疲惫了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "就算不是为了前男友，你也不一定会当导游",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "对啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我受不了那些奇葩，消耗我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，挣的钱不够治结节",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我也当不了导游",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "可以预想到会接触很多蠢人...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你也厌蠢吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个世上很难有人不厌蠢吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你有没有觉得我很蠢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是说感情的事吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不会以感情去评判别人是蠢还是聪明",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "这哪说的清啊，我只是旁观者",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "不对，我连旁观者都算不上，是旁听",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我感觉现在好多了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "。别人说话我能听进去一点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你还记得我们刚才的刚才聊的话题是什么吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "奶茶啊，你还没告诉我让你心情变好的奶茶是什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "霸王茶姬的糯糯青山",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "告辞了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我消受不起",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "很好喝呀！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我真觉得有股狗狗jio味",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你好没有品",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "明明是很清香的味道",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "青山应该就是奶茶界的香菜吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你也不吃香菜吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我对香菜的态度比较中立？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "不会特意去吃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是真的出现在餐桌上，我也不会有很大的反应",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "不然我觉得对爱吃香菜的人来说太不礼貌了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你真的是很有礼貌了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我就很爱吃香菜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    }
